##It's been 14 days, and our lives are still going on | Sandwich Wuhan Daily Book 11

WECHAT china30s

Feature description, a platform that encourages you to write about your life. Founded in March 2011, it has a sandwich writing school and a media platform, China Sandwich, at the same time, we are committed to applying the story to cross-border product design, urban culture excavation, exhibition fair, space creation and other three-dimensional field.

For people in and around the walled city of Wuhan, the sense of community has never been stronger, and "isolation" has become a key word in life. In today's "Wuhan Daily" Book of the day, the three authors present to you the true feeling of living in an infected area. Behind the increase in diagnoses and suspicious data are scarce medical resources, tense neighborhoods, and "important notices" being posted everywhere... when there are confirmed cases in the community, no one can pull out.

01

The community says,
There's no room. Let's go home and Quarantine

By Huang Beibei
Coordinates: Wuhan, Hankou
Occupation: Teacher

In the last two days, I've seen a case close to me, not enough to require an ICU, but enough to know what you'd be dealing with if you were currently sick. It's cold, and it's scary.

This person is the ex-husband of the friend, cold a few days, originally said to get better, the day before yesterday suddenly have a fever add suck difficulty. He rode for half an hour to the west wing of the Fourth Hospital. The CT results were "ground glass, " "double lung infection, " "viral pneumonia, " but the doctor said there was no box, no diagnosis, so he wasn't even a probable case, so he went home and quarantined.

He was in his sister's home when the New Year, he is not aware of this time also gathered, the family even adults with children seven or eight people, has infected his father. To send the rest of them back to their homes in Wuchang, where Wuchang might be better off, with more medical resources, but no cars. Friends want to borrow my car, my husband and I take two cars out, do not contact, and then drive a car back. I thought about it for a long time, but I didn't dare to borrow it. I felt guilty.

Yesterday I heard that the community began to quarantine, rushed to the queue, for several hours, the community said, no place, let home quarantine, not mandatory quarantine? The CT results are useless. According to the community, arrangements can only be made if someone goes to the hospital at the isolation point and takes up a bed, or if someone dies.

There are four types of people in the article no. 10 issued by Wuhan. The first type of confirmed cases refers to those who have boxes and beds; the second type of suspected cases refers to those who are seriously ill and who first put you in and then test you with boxes; the third type of fever cases, that's the case I'm talking about, where the CT scan didn't show the confirmed cases; the fourth category is the close contacts of the confirmed patients. In the third group, people say they want to keep communities isolated, but the situation is completely different in different communities, Wuchang may be better, at least it can keep them separated from their families, Hankou doesn't know what's going on, there aren't enough places to keep them apart, shouldn't we find another hotel?

At present, Hubei said the number of confirmed and suspected, in addition to this, there are huge fever crowd, had a CT, infected with pneumonia, but can not be confirmed, these people are not included in the statistics, how much will the number be? Now each community has announced the number of cases of fever, but a total number of communities? How many neighborhoods does that make in the city?

See the field not only fever cases, even with the case has been in contact with strict isolation, Wuhan local, even fever cases are not included in the isolation point, let Wuhan people how to think? In the face of this mortality rate, for some people, waiting to die may not be an exaggeration.

02

In the community,
The Horn blared from morning till night

By Shanshan
COORDINATES: Hubei, Yichang
Occupation: Marketing

Something will happen, the community down the case, followed by a large number of suspected patients, as well as the whole block block and access restrictions. In the community, from morning till night, the loudspeakers sounded all day, which consisted of people returning from Wuhan reporting to the police, taking their temperature every day, telling grid members in the community, and repeating don't go out.

"Fifty people have returned from Wuhan, " he said. "starting in the evening, all exits, from sidewalks to garages, are closed. To go round the house is to kill each other. To party is to commit suicide. If you need to buy food, each family can only send one member of the family to do the shopping every two days, the hypervigilant mother had already barred the family from going out, but with the actual ban, the psychological plague was one step closer, prompting the family's fear of food shortages. My mother began asking questions about the way to buy food in various groups and was recommended by a community group to a shopping group in JD.com.

After a while, my mother hesitated in front of the Living Room and looked around the window as if she was waiting for her "right" . My mother said to him through the heavy glass. "I won't come out without my mask. You can leave it by the glass door. I'll transfer the money to you. "

Then he opened wechat and began to transfer money, mouth also kept muttering, "you sure it is so much money right, 119.5, ah so expensive, you see have received Ah. "

A minute after his departure, his mother discreetly pulled on her thin blue plastic cooking mask, mask and sunglasses, pursed her lips and took a deep breath, and rushed to the floor to get the heavy "token" , shut the door again immediately, take off shoe, rush into kitchen long breath"suffocate me".

Before I could remind her to wash her hands, she started muttering, "why is this so light? I bought 10 kilos of flour. Look, it's only 2.5 kilos, 5 kilos. What's going on? " Was told that the supermarket price has increased, but did not have time to inform led to the Oolong.

"It's depressing, " he said. "I'll tell my neighbors and friends that it's a real rip-off. "

"Mom, it's a good time to have flour to sell. On the other hand, you can have delicious steamed buns in the morning. "

After listening to my comfort, she confidently took out 5 Jins of flour, "that is not, your mother's red dumplings is a top delicious. "

So, at 22:00 in the evening, for my brother cooked a bowl of old pickled cabbage Kimchi after midnight snack, pull me, together began to knead the noodles, really can not stop the mother.

03

Community workers,
Separate the street with a rope and a bicycle

By Cast
COORDINATES: Huangshi, Hubei
Occupation: Screenwriter Douyin

Grandma old, plus last night before going to bed to wolfberry, astragalus and Jujube water drink, because the water did not bubble open, eat bad belly, midnight pain of the get up and spit on the ground.

Waking me from my sleep, I began to wonder if this particular time..

Since the declaration of the city closures, I have procured all the medical and daily necessities for the family, and she has been in the House for at least ten days, so it would have been impossible for her to have had any contact with the source of the infection, except for me. But I went out three times wearing a mask, back home is also frequent hand washing and disinfection, and test temperature is normal, normal body, except for more like to sleep than in the past, there is nothing unusual. So I'm guessing grandma's less likely to get the new pneumonia.

And father, aunt to discuss out to buy stomach medicine and hand-warmer bags, in the commercial parity in many people in the queue for food, we are ready to continue to live in a snail's nest, stay at home to insist on a long war.

Luckily, I don't have a lot of stuff, so I can just scan it, pay for it, and get out of here.

When I came back, I found some community workers wearing rainproof clothes as isolation clothes, using ropes and bicycles to separate the streets of Shengyang port, where we live.

It was advertised that people would wear masks outside, but there were still people who did only the superficial work, sitting and chatting in the small square in front of the door.

I don't know. Did the guy who was sitting here taking off his mask notice the sign next to it? It's better to wear a mask than a respirator, and it's better to be at home than lying in the ICU.

Ignorance and fluke how terrible, but some people do not take it seriously, the virus needs to find a host, no one knows whether it will be their own. Before going home, grandma home next to a new confirmed case, two confirmed cases of two buildings, the community posted notice, warning, and pull up the cordon warning isolation.

A few days later, the access roads to the community had been boarded up.

Apart from the sun, the deserted streets, apart from the epidemic prevention staff and community workers, have been no movement.

In the evening, after seeing my father's new news, the store was forced to close its doors after three sales staff showed that they had been diagnosed with the new pneumonia virus. Once a major supermarket closes because of an infection, that means more people will flock to other supermarkets to snap up the necessities of life. It also means a second transmission, three transmission has already begun, life will be even harder for people in the affected areas.

But we are not afraid, in the face of the virus this invisible enemy, our local government decided to 9:00-11:00 pm on the city disinfection, this is an unprecedented city clearance operation. Grandma says she's lived more than 80 years without ever seeing it. We have no desire to live, and hope that after the plague we can not only lead by example, but also devote more energy and resources to the study of the virus.
